citation.case_name: Weber, Interim District Director, Bureau of Immigration and Customs Enforcement v. Phu Chan Hoang

html:
538 U.S. 1010

WEBER, INTERIM DISTRICT DIRECTOR, BUREAU OF IMMIGRATION AND CUSTOMS ENFORCEMENT
v.
PHU CHAN HOANG ET AL.

No. 01-1616.

Supreme Court of United States.

May 5, 2003.

1

CERTIORARI TO THE UNITED STATES COURT OF APPEALS FOR THE TENTH CIRCUIT.

2

C. A. 10th Cir. Certiorari granted, judgment vacated, and case remanded for further consideration in light of Demore v. Kim, ante, p. 510. Reported below: 282 F. 3d 1247.
